creator: TSVB
descriptionHtml:
As a delivery person at getDukan, you earn money for each order you deliver to customers in Kuwait. Not just that, delivery partners at getDukan enjoy a host of benefits such as flexibility to choose between a full-time and part-time job, tips from customers and more.

You will get lots of benefits as a getDukan Delivery Person App:
-You can work at your choosing time
-Earn more with more delivery
-Get your income weekly, monthly
-Use Google map navigation for search delivery address
-Manage the new ride/delivery request – accept/reject
-Call to user’s with a single tap
-Chat with a user within the app
-Get the tips from customers
-View feedback with the user all details provided

Want to join us as a Delivery Partner? Install the app now!
